{"tid":2369762,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"39 歲中大支那人「食祭品」教授李薇疑用長者八達通斷正，怒轟港鐵職員「資本家走狗」","createTime":"2021-01-17T12:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T06:51:48.000Z","uid":173921,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e8378871d8de98b31f0527434310bb0ac5b0e926","tid":2369762,"uid":173921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T12:06:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20210117-26_A4xbG_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20210117-26_A4xbG_1200x0.png&h=fbdeff87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日網上流傳影片，顯示一名婦人疑被揭發使用長者八達通後，與港鐵職員爆發爭執。有指涉事婦人是早前因「食祭品」引發熱議、39歲的中大政治及行政學系助理教授李薇。李薇回覆《立場》時，拒正面回應是否當事人，反斥傳媒「八卦」。她又批評政府沒有機制讓不符合「2 元優惠」的低收入人士受惠。警方則證實，一名 39 歲李姓女子昨日（16日）因使用特惠八達通，違反港鐵附例而票控。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/39-%E6%AD%B2%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7-%E9%A3%9F%E7%A5%AD%E5%93%81-%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88-%E7%96%91%E7%94%A8%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E5%85%AB%E9%81%94%E9%80%9A%E6%96%B7%E6%AD%A3-%E6%80%92%E8%BD%9F%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1-%E8%B3%87%E6%9C%AC%E5%AE%B6%E8%B5%B0%E7%8B%97/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F39-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7-%25E9%25A3%259F%25E7%25A5%25AD%25E5%2593%2581-%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%258E%2588-%25E7%2596%2591%25E7%2594%25A8%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%2585%25AB%25E9%2581%2594%25E9%2580%259A%25E6%2596%25B7%25E6%25AD%25A3-%25E6%2580%2592%25E8%25BD%259F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E7%258B%2597%2F&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHBYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=18e3b440\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F39-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7-%25E9%25A3%259F%25E7%25A5%25AD%25E5%2593%2581-%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%258E%2588-%25E7%2596%2591%25E7%259